WEBVTT

00:00:01.809 --> 00:00:06.129
The idea of eliminating poverty
is a great goal.

00:00:07.026 --> 00:00:09.806
I don't think anyone
in this room would disagree.

00:00:10.512 --> 00:00:15.036
What worries me
is when politicians with money

00:00:15.060 --> 00:00:17.681
and charismatic rock stars --

00:00:17.705 --> 00:00:19.285
(Laughter)

00:00:19.309 --> 00:00:20.626
use the words,

00:00:20.650 --> 00:00:24.819
" ... it all just sounds so, so simple."

00:00:27.073 --> 00:00:30.165
Now, I've got no bucket of money today